      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a reliable daily driver. While it remains mechanically sound and ready for the road, the exterior shows clear signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and general wear from regular use. All major features are functional, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. This is an ideal choice for someone seeking a dependable, budget-friendly vehicle who isn't concerned with minor cosmetic flaws.",
