    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, this unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands excellence without compromise. Every detail reflects a standard of care that ensures both prestige and performance.",
