    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute beauty with you. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and pampered every single day. You won't find a single blemish on it\u2014it's truly in flawless, pristine condition inside and out. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know you're going to have the best time behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
