      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you! It's been my pride and joy, and I know you're going to love it. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
