    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a superlative example of naturally aspirated precision. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear 333 hp with a soaring 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring documented preventative subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive service history detailing recent rod bearing and VANOS overhauls. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the paint depth and clarity are concours-level, complemented by a pristine Nappa leather interior. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
